room_title: Escape room "Diamond Heist" by Escape Thrill in Tampa
room_description: You and your crew have been framed for stealing the blue “Star of Infinity” diamond, a rare blue diamond recently unearthed in South Africa. Experts believe it’s the most valuable diamond ever. It was stolen by a masked gunman hired by organized crime leader Quentin Ortiz and is being housed in his secure vault that is protected by multiple security mechanisms, including high-intensity lasers. It’s up to your crew to secure the diamond before Ortiz’s is alerted and clear your names.
